name: dfs.qjournal.finalize-segment.timeout.ms
description:
Quorum timeout in milliseconds during finalizing for a specific
    segment.

name: mapreduce.job.speculative.retry-after-speculate
description:
The waiting time(ms) to do next round of speculation
  if there are tasks speculated in this round.

name: mapreduce.job.local-fs.single-disk-limit.check.interval-ms
description: Interval of disk limit check to run in ms.

name: dfs.namenode.decommission.interval
description:
Namenode periodicity in seconds to check if
    decommission or maintenance is complete. Support multiple time unit
    suffix(case insensitive), as described in dfs.heartbeat.interval.
    If no time unit is specified then seconds is assumed.

name: dfs.namenode.edekcacheloader.interval.ms
description:
When KeyProvider is configured, the interval time of warming
    up edek cache on NN starts up / becomes active. All edeks will be loaded
    from KMS into provider cache. The edek cache loader will try to warm up the
    cache until succeed or NN leaves active state.
